+- Verify no placeholder text remains in docs or release assets
+
+## Sanity checks
+
+- README reflects the current release line
+- `docs/GETTING_STARTED.md` and `docs/README_FIRST.txt` agree
+- license files reflect the intended release state
+- security docs do not contain placeholder contact text
+- changelog entry exists for the release being published
+
+## Publish
+
+- Create GitHub release
+- Attach installer
+- Attach checksum file
+- Attach any profile / routing bundles intended for the release
